"title": "5387: leisure, and pastimes",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5387: leisure, and pastimes",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture gives examples of many different kinds of leisure activity.</p>\n<h2>Necessary leisure activities</h2>\n<h2>Sleeping</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps127:2\">PSA 127:2</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:12\">ECC 5:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps4:8\">PSA 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:38\">MRK 4:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:6\">ACT 12:6</a></p>\n<h3>Eating and drinking</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:54\">GEN 24:54</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:13\">ECC 3:13</a></p>\n<h2>Pleasurable pastimes</h2>\n<h3>Hospitality</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:3-Gen18:5\">GEN 18:3–18:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:9\">1PE 4:9</a></p>\n<h3>Feasting</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:15\">1KI 3:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh8:10\">NEH 8:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth8:17\">EST 8:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:4\">JOB 1:4</a></p>\n<h3>Music</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:23\">1SA 16:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:16-1Sam16:18\">1SA 16:16–16:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs3:14-2Kgs3:15\">2KI 3:14–3:15</a></p>\n<h3>Dancing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:4\">ECC 3:4</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:20\">EXO 15:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg11:34\">JDG 11:34</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:6\">1SA 18:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job21:11\">JOB 21:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:4\">JER 31:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg21:19-Judg21:21\">JDG 21:19–21:21</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:22\">MRK 6:22</a> <em>dancing in revelry</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:14-2Sam6:16\">2SA 6:14–6:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:21\">2SA 6:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps149:3\">PSA 149:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps150:4\">PSA 150:4</a></p>\n<h3>Physical recreation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:8\">1TI 4:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:24-1Cor9:27\">1CO 9:24–9:27</a> <em>Although Paul never mentions Christians taking part in the games (which were often associated with pagan festivals), he does show an appreciation of the discipline necessary</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:5\">2TI 2:5</a></p>\n<h3>Gardening</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:5-Eccl2:6\">ECC 2:5–2:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:15\">GEN 2:15</a></p>\n<h3>Enjoyment of nature</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps8:3\">PSA 8:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:10-Ps104:14\">PSA 104:10–104:14</a></p>\n<h3>Sightseeing</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:1\">MRK 13:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:16\">ACT 17:16</a></p>\n<h3>Education and literature</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl1:13\">ECC 1:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:32-1Kgs4:34\">1KI 4:32–4:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth6:1\">EST 6:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:5\">PRO 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:12\">ECC 12:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:21\">ACT 17:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:13\">2TI 4:13</a></p>\n<h3>Children's games</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:5\">ZEC 8:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:16-Matt11:17\">MAT 11:16–11:17</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:32\">LUK 7:32</a></p>\n<h2>Harmful pastimes</h2>\n<h3>Licentious amusements</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:3\">1PE 4:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:20-Gen9:21\">GEN 9:20–9:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:19\">EXO 32:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:29-Prov23:30\">PRO 23:29–23:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:13\">ROM 13:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:4\">EPH 5:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:12\">EPH 5:12</a></p>\n<h3>Cruel amusements</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:25\">JDG 16:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam2:14\">2SA 2:14</a></p>",
